Epoch:    14
Version:  1.10.5
Release:  2%{?dist}
Summary:  A system-independent interface for user-level packet capture
License:  ISC AND BSD-2-Clause AND BSD-3-Clause AND BSD-4-Clause-UC
URL:      https://www.tcpdump.org/

